snippet.title: HeyMan Trailer 2
snippet.description:
"Hey, Man! - Born in the Electric" is a fun 2D platform puzzle game in which a main character born by electricity in a city ventures to find what he sees. The game will provide users with a new experience with interesting stories and unique gameplay.

Steam Game
